sentences: Annika Schmarsel (born 8 July 1993) known by her stage name Alice Ivy,  is an Australian electronic musician and producer.
Alice Ivy was the winner of the 2016 Triple J Unearthed Listen Out competition.
She has released two studio albums: I'm Dreaming (2018), and Don't Sleep (2020),  which reached No. 77 on the ARIA Albums Chart.
She has released two studio albums: I'm Dreaming (2018), and Don't Sleep (2020),  which reached No. 77 on the ARIA Albums Chart.
Annika Schmarsel was born in 1993 to West German immigrants who settled in Geelong in 1987.
